    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure all male public toilets have baby changing facilities",
        "additional_details": "When a male parent takes their child out or even when with a female partner, the changing facilities shouldn\u2019t be only available in the female toilets.\r\n\r\nIt should not be solely down for the female to change the child or to have the option to change the child.",
        "background": "Ensure that baby changing facilities are available for all male parents to access. \r\n\r\nProvide legislation to ensure male parents are able to change their child in the privacy of a toilet or room. Too often changing facilities are only available in female toilets.",
